{"tid":411882,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"決意離開拉登,這是我最後一個貼","createTime":"2017-09-24T07:46:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-27T12:02:31.000Z","uid":80183,"like":4,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d06621eab45827c01f9580efbf76c321245f1e3e","tid":411882,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T07:46:54.000Z","msg":"拉登尼度認識左好多好朋友同g(有村,kathy,麻友等等)<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n現實既我真係好失敗<br />\n冇女冇朋友冇錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個人灰到想縮埋一舊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我諗如果我死個時<br />\n除左屋企人外<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n應該無咩人會掛住我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好彩有你地同我吠<br />\n多謝你地同我渡過人生最後既時光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔使挽留<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f835b63e7babf2ae8a001210e89e8f14420cb98","tid":411882,"uid":88120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T07:48:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"058c1707872f7301e8cb4105fcf2f98290ba9cfe","tid":411882,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T07:48:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>88,rip</blockquote><br />\n88吉岡<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c3f8bf436bffffca0cadd2a8cb690b3a44f27c4","tid":411882,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T07:50:41.000Z","msg":"886"},{"pid":"283427ad70943292a6773b38cc851e11e75f1ee2","tid":411882,"uid":80183,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T07:51:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>886</blockquote><br />\n88香川子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c